    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/science-and-innovation-network-annual-report-2011-12--2"/>
    <title>Science and innovation network: annual report 2011 - 12</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Report of the work of the global Foreign &amp;amp; Commonwealth Office and Department for Business science and innovation network.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Highlights the achievements of the network, which uses contacts to monitor global scientific developments and build new relationships and collaborations. It showcases examples of UK work to influence and learn from science and innovation policy internationally, and also facilitate international collaboration to the benefit of the UK.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
